Module AppointmentSchedulerApp
Package me.stevensheaves.data.model

Class Appointment

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.stevensheaves.data.model.Appointment
  • public class Appointment
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used in holding all data for an appointment. There are multiple constructors in the class to account for the multiple use cases where not all data may be available or required.
